Let Whirligig help you improve your quality of life. Whatever your
health goals, Whirligig can send reminders by email or cell phone text
message reminding you to take medication, exercise, drink 64 ounces of
water, or work on your stress level. You set the frequency of
reminders, and let Whirligig spur you on to meet your goals.

Keep your New Year's resolutions with Whirligig!
